) I also write a proprietary library used in the pre-processing of concrete 3d printing. 

I am also slowly learning APL (Dyalog). While I haven't implemented the Space Group library in APL yet, I got into it because it is trivial to generate the 3d matrices for the library with APL. I have since fallen in love with the other aspects of the language.

I'm really excited to be part of the FoC community - I think it's one of the most interesting and creative spaces in computation today.
